  {
    "text": "讀書破萬卷，下筆如有神",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "學海無涯，唯勤是岸",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "千里之行，始於足下",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "不積跬步，無以至千里",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "天行健，君子以自強不息",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "地勢坤，君子以厚德載物",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "三人行，必有我師焉",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "己所不欲，勿施於人",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "學而時習之，不亦說乎",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "知之為知之，不知為不知",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "溫故而知新，可以為師矣",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "敏而好學，不恥下問",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "君子和而不同",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "仁者愛人",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "禮之用，和為貴",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "信近於義，言可復也",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "恭近於禮，遠恥辱也",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "君子求諸己，小人求諸人",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "古之學者為己，今之學者為人",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "士不可以不弘毅，任重而道遠",
    "source": "literature"
  },
  {
    "text": "你最近點樣啊",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "我幾好，你呢",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "我都唔錯，多謝關心",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "聽日有冇時間一齊食飯",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "好呀，幾點喺邊度等",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "七點半喺地鐵站見",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "冇問題，到時見",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "你鍾意食咩嘢",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "我鍾意食廣東菜",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "我都係，尤其係點心",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "嗰間酒樓啲點心好出名",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "咁我哋就去嗰度啦",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "好，就咁決定",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "你最近有冇睇戲",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "有呀，睇咗套好精彩嘅戲",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "講嚟聽吓",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "係講緊一個追夢嘅故事",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "聽落好似幾有意思",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "係呀，好勵志㗎",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
  {
    "text": "咁我都想去睇",
    "source": "dialogue"
  },
