  {
    "text": "早晨，今日天气好好",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "食咗饭未？一齐去饮茶啦",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "唔该，请问呢度点去",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我今日好开心，因为见到老朋友",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "听日放假，打算去行山",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢间餐厅啲烧鹅好出名",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我要两个叉烧包同埋一杯热奶茶",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "唔该帮我影张相，谢谢",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢个星期好忙，日日加班",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "周末约咗朋友睇戏",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我最近学紧煲汤，好好饮",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢件衫好靓，几多钱？",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "多谢你嘅帮忙，我好感激",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "听日要早起，今晚早点瞓",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我哋一齐去行街买嘢啦",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢度啲风景真系好靓",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我中意食朱古力同雪糕",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "最近天气好热，记得饮水",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢本书好好睇，推荐俾你",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我哋下次再约食饭",
    "source": "daily",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "人生有幾多個十年，最緊要係開心",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "做人要有骨氣，唔可以輕易放棄",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "珍惜眼前人，活在當下",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "友誼永固，感謝有你",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "堅持到底，就一定會成功",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "夢想係要靠自己雙手去實現",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "笑一笑，世界更美好",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "愛要及時，唔好等失去先後悔",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "仁者愛人，禮者敬人",
    "source": "culture",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "你好，請問你叫咩名？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我叫小明，你呢？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我係阿華，好高興認識你",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "你最近點樣？有冇去旅行？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我上個月去咗日本，好開心",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "日本有咩好玩？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我去咗東京同大阪，食咗好多好嘢",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "聽落好正！我都想去",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "下次我哋可以一齊去",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "好呀！一言為定",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "你平時有咩興趣？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我鍾意影相同煮嘢食",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我都鍾意煮嘢，可以交流下",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "好提議！我整幾味俾你試下",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "真係？我好期待！",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "你平時去開邊度買餸？",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我去街市買，新鮮啲",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我都覺得街市啲嘢新鮮",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "下次一齊去買餸啦",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "好，就咁決定！",
    "source": "dialogue",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "今日去咗一間新開嘅茶餐廳，啲奶茶好飲",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "呢間酒樓嘅點心好出名，蝦餃燒賣好正",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "我中意食乾炒牛河，夠鑊氣",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "煲仔飯冬天食最暖胃",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "雲吞麵係香港特色美食",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "蛋撻配奶茶，經典下午茶",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "菠蘿包加牛油，簡單又美味",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "咖喱魚蛋係街頭小食之王",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "雞蛋仔外脆內軟，好受歡迎",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "格仔餅加煉奶花生醬，回味無窮",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "腸粉滑溜，配甜醬麻醬最夾",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "燒鵝皮脆肉嫩，必食推介",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "臘味煲仔飯香噴噴，令人垂涎",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "西多士配糖漿，邪惡又滿足",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "車仔麵可以自由配搭，好方便",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "避風塘炒蟹好惹味，辣得好過癮",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "楊枝甘露清甜解渴，夏天最啱",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "紅豆沙糖水暖胃又暖心",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "芝麻糊香甜濃郁，傳統糖水",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  },
  {
    "text": "薑汁湯圓暖身又甜蜜",
    "source": "food",
    "collected_at": "2026-07-04T16:38:20.885922"
  }
]